FT  03 JUN 94 / UK Company News: Bunzl
Bunzl, the distribution and cigarette filters group, has acquired Marstan, a
US distributor of paper and plastic disposable items.
The consideration of Dollars 11.5m (Pounds 7.6m) cash payable on completion
is subject to adjustment up to a maximum of Dollars 1m, dependent on the
level of net assets acquired.
A further profits-related payment of up to Dollars 2.55m may become payable
subject to the company's performance over a three-year period.
